Enum Class Role

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Role>
org.jboss.elemento.Role
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Role>, Constable
public enum Role extends Enum<Role>
Roles as recommended by the MDN. This is a subset of all possible roles defined by the W3C.
